item.title: My projects
item.description:
Eco Life Javascript, Firebase,SPA, Flexbox. January 2020. Social Network that allows any user to create an access account, log in with it; create, edit, delete and “likear” publications. Write Notes Javascript, Node.js, Jest. February 2020 It is a tool that uses Node.js, which reads and analyzes files in Markdown format, to verify the links they contain and report some statistics.
Data Lovers Javascript, Node.
